nd, applied to men,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhiruwna","text_ar":"طَاهِرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and (of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TahirN","text_ar":"طَهِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tahiruwna","text_ar":"طَهِرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) the only form; there being no broken pl.: (TA:) and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhirapN","text_ar":"طَاهِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhiraAtN","text_ar":"طَاهِرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaAhiru","text_ar":"طَوَاهِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN TaAhirN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ طَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TahiyrN","text_ar":"طَهِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A clean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pure, man"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN TaAhirapN mina Aln~ajaAsapi","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ طَاهِرَةٌ مِنَ النَّجَاسَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman pure from dirt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N TaAhirN","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ طَاهِرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pure, water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fit to cleanse"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purify with."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viyaAbN TahaAraY","text_ar":"ثِيَابٌ طَهَارَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clean clothes"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TahuwrN","text_ar":"طَهُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pure from the menstrual discharge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this sense without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar:) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhirN mina AlHayoDi","text_ar":"طَاهِرٌ مِنَ الحَيْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa TaAhiru AlEiroDi","text_ar":"هُوَ طَاهِرُ العِرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is clear from vice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN TaAhirapN mina AlEuyuwbi","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ طَاهِرَةٌ مِنَ العُيُوبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman pure from vices,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN TaAhiru Alv~iyaAbi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ طَاهِرُ الثِّيَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhiru AlA^avowaAbi","text_ar":"طَاهِرُ الاَثْوَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far-removed, from low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignoble, habits:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, TA:) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhiru Alxuluqi","text_ar":"طَاهِرُ الخُلُقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxuluqi","text_ar":"الخُلُقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tahiru","text_ar":"طَهِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAhirap","text_ar":"طَاهِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IAar","K","M","S","A","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%B1/","headword_ar":"طاهر","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23381#989d52","body_html":"<span>الطاهر: من عصمه الله تعالى من المخالفات.<br></span><br>الطاهر الظاهر: من عصمه الله من المعاصي.<br><br>الطاهر الباطن: من عصمه الله تعالى من الوساوس والهواجس.<br><br>الطاهر السر: من لا يذهل عن الله طرفة عين.<br><br>الطاهر السر والعلانية: من قام بتوفية حقوق الحق والخلق جميعًا؛ لسعته برعاية الجانبين."}]}}